title: Led Zeppelin - 1969.03.03 London, Playhouse Theatre
description:
Led Zeppelin - 1969.03.03 London, Playhouse Theatre   

MARCH 3, 1969 - TOP GEAR, PLAYHOUSE THEATRE, WESTMINSTER, LONDON, ENGLAND 
(MONDAY, recording session between 2pm and 6pm)

Source: 
Complete superb professional pre-FM radio recording. 19 minutes.

Details: 
The tape is an excellent radio master.

Tracklist:
01 - You Shook Me
02 - Communication Breakdown
03 - I Can't Quit You Baby
04 - Dazed And Confused

Comments: 
Debut radio appearance and a great delight for ears! A classic, 
early Zeppelin in the best form. Robert hints some incredible 
notes during I Can't Quit You Baby. All songs were played very 
close to the album versions which caused powerful and raw sound
